one-on-one.''
   It couldn't immediately be learned if Bakker was listening to
the program. The Bakkers said Tuesday they would delay the daily
taping of their ``Jim and Tammy'' show until late this afternoon to
avoid Ms. Hahn and the hoopla surrounding her.
