2,453.45.
   Declining issues outnumbered advances by about 7 to 6 in
nationwide trading of NYSE-listed issues, with 791 down, 677 up and
500 unchanged.
   Big Board volume came to 173.10 million shares, down from 179.35
million in the previous session.
